Set renderer/rendering_method=gl_compatibility. Forward+ was defaulting, compiling 60+ 3D shader caches (SSAO, SSR, VoxelGI, volumetric fog) for a pure 2D game. GL Compatibility is the lightest renderer, matches hardware floor (integrated graphics), and has zero visual difference for 2D CanvasItem rendering.
